name: Gift Voucher - Any Amount
description:
Love the illustrations but not sure which one is best suited to your recipient? Why not buy them a gift voucher!

Sent via email or specially packaged and sent via post, our gift vouchers are a delight to send or receive.

Available in any amount (amounts other than what are shown below are available - please email me and I will create a custom order for you), the gift vouchers are available from 12 months from the date of purchase and any unused amounts will remain valid until this date.

Ideal for baby showers, birthdays and maternity leave gifts!

Sending your voucher:
Once you have ordered and paid for your voucher via paypal, I will send an email confirmation to the purchaser requesting information about where to send the voucher. 
Please state in the email which method you would like the voucher to be sent (email or post) and information regarding the recipient's email or postal address. 

A short message to the recipient can also be included with the voucher.

All details of both the purchaser and recipient will remain confidential.

Redeeming the voucher:
Once the recipient has received their voucher, they have 12 months in which to redeem their gift at the Little Skipper online shop. Each voucher will contain a unique voucher code which can be typed in during the checkout process and the gift voucher amount will be automatically deducted from the checkout price.

Email me if you have any further questions: info@littleskipper.com.au

Enjoy!

name: Large Alphabet Print - Bold or pastel colours
description:
A stunning, colourful alphabet print filled with animals from A - Z!

This large size print is created from an original hand-drawn artwork by Sally Gross of Winter Avenue Press.

It comes in 2 colour combinations - Pastel colours or bold colours.

Each print is professionally printed on archival quality bamboo/cotton fine art paper. It is A3 size, meaning it will fit within a standard 11" x 14" frame window with extra room around the edge for framing.

All prints are hand-signed by the artist.

We only print on 290gsm Hahnemuhle Bamboo/Cotton Fine Art Paper. Made  from 90% bamboo fibres & 10% cotton, it is good for the environment  and guarantees archival standards whilst preserving the special touch  and feel of genuine art paper. Our inks are water based, environmentally friendly and of  archival quality.

All items illustrated and printed in Australia.

A3 Print Unframed : image fits within 28 x 35cm or 11" x 14".

name: Small Art Prints in Mount - Various Illustrations
description:
Archival-quality Giclee prints created from original hand-drawn artworks by Sally Gross of Winter Avenue Press.

Each print is signed and comes in a white mount mat ready to pop into your favourite frame.

Image is printed on an A5 size sheet fitted inside a standard-sized 8" x 10" white mount mat. The window of the mount (image size) is 12 x 17cm.

We only print on 290gsm Hahnemuhle Bamboo/Cotton Fine Art Paper. Made from 90% bamboo fibres & 10% cotton, it is good for the environment and guarantees archival standards whilst preserving the special touch and feel of genuine art paper.

All items illustrated and printed in Australia.

Price includes Free Postage Australia-Wide.

Also available in bigger sizes - see my other listings or contact me for details!
